  "text": "MicroPET/CT scans revealed that the radioactivity of the two radiation sources were roughly the same ( Figure 4A ). The results of optical imaging showed that the emission intensity of both [CITATION_1] F-FDG with REMPs and 18 F-FDG alone decreased with increasing depth from the top surface of the phantoms to the center axel of the holes. The maximum penetration of [CITATION_2] F-FDG with REMPs reached up to 15 mm, while [CITATION_3] F-FDG alone had a maximum penetration of around 5 mm ( Figure 4B and 4C) .",
